==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superseminate
<hw>Su`per*sem"i*nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To sow,
as seed, over something previously sown.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>That can not be done with joy, when it shall be indifferent to any
man to <qex>superseminate</qex> what he please.</q> <rj><qau>Jer.
Taylor.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Supersemination</ent>⟦br⟧
